## Export Tooling

This repo also contains tooling to export PyTorch models to ONNX:

```bash
cd export/hycoclip
uv run python export_onnx.py --checkpoint model.pth --onnx model.onnx
```

See [export/hycoclip/README.md](export/hycoclip/README.md) for details.

